インタフェース Codec<T>

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    ConditionCodec, FulfillmentCodec, InterledgerAddressCodec, InterledgerPacketCodec<T>, InterledgerPacketTypeCodec, InterledgerPaymentCodec, InterledgerPaymentRequestCodec, InterledgerProtocolErrorCodec, PskMessageCodec, QuoteByDestinationAmountRequestCodec, QuoteByDestinationAmountResponseCodec, QuoteBySourceAmountRequestCodec, QuoteBySourceAmountResponseCodec, QuoteLiquidityRequestCodec, QuoteLiquidityResponseCodec
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    AbstractCodec, ConditionOerCodec, FulfillmentOerCodec, InterledgerAddressOerCodec, InterledgerPacketTypeOerCodec, InterledgerPaymentOerCodec, InterledgerPaymentRequestOerCodec, InterledgerProtocolProtocolErrorOerCodec, OerGeneralizedTimeCodec, OerIA5StringCodec, OerLengthPrefixCodec, OerOctetStringCodec, OerSequenceOfAddressCodec, OerUint256Codec, OerUint32Codec, OerUint64Codec, OerUint8Codec, PskMessageBinaryCodec, QuoteByDestinationAmountRequestOerCodec, QuoteByDestinationAmountResponseOerCodec, QuoteBySourceAmountRequestOerCodec, QuoteBySourceAmountResponseOerCodec, QuoteLiquidityRequestOerCodec, QuoteLiquidityResponseOerCodec

    public interface Codec<T>
    A generic coder/decoder interface for all Interledger objects.

    • メソッドのサマリー

      すべてのメソッド インスタンス・メソッド abstractメソッド デフォルト・メソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      T read(CodecContext context, InputStream inputStream)
      Read an object from the buffer according to the rules defined in the CodecContext.
      void write(CodecContext context, T instance, OutputStream outputStream)
      Write an object to the outputStream according to the rules defined in the context.
      default void writeObject(CodecContext context, Object instance, OutputStream outputStream)
      Writes an Object to the outputStream by attempting to convert it to a proper type.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • read

        T read(CodecContext context,
       InputStream inputStream)
throws IOException
        Read an object from the buffer according to the rules defined in the CodecContext.
        パラメータ:
        context - An instance of CodecContext.
        inputStream - An instance of InputStream to read data from.
        戻り値:
        An instance of T as decoded from inputStream.
        例外:
        IOException - If anything goes wrong reading from the InputStream.

      • write

        void write(CodecContext context,
           T instance,
           OutputStream outputStream)
    throws IOException
        Write an object to the outputStream according to the rules defined in the context.
        パラメータ:
        context - An instance of CodecContext.
        instance - An instance of type T.
        outputStream - An instance of OutputStream to write data to.
        例外:
        IOException - If anything goes wrong writing to the OutputStream

      • writeObject

        default void writeObject(CodecContext context,
                         Object instance,
                         OutputStream outputStream)
                  throws IOException
        Writes an Object to the outputStream by attempting to convert it to a proper type.
        パラメータ:
        context - An instance of CodecContext.
        instance - An instance of type Object.
        outputStream - An instance of OutputStream to write data to.
        例外:
        IOException - If anything goes wrong writing to the OutputStream
